channel.title: Comments on: Google realizes that JavaScript is a dead end programming language, to be replaced by Dart a new language
channel.description: A Technical Community for IT Professionals

item.title: By: Amelia @ IT Management
item.dc:creator: Amelia @ IT Management
item.content:encoded:
We’ve all gotten used to Java. However, Java does have its limitations. I’m glad that they’re thinking of something.

I have my doubts, though. Until this new language is out, I’m keeping my excitement down.
